N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1155.5 - Parking

State Regulations

No person shall park an aircraft, watercraft or motor vehicle
or leave the same standing except at such places as may be prescribed or
permitted by the manager. Notes
